<p>You may be able to get help with the cost of travel for surgery and surgical consultations. Further information about travel costs can be found:</p>
<ul>
  <li>on <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/using-the-nhs/help-with-health-costs/healthcare-travel-costs-scheme-htcs/">the NHS website</a> (valid across the whole of the UK)</li>
  <li>on <a href="https://gov.wales/low-income-scheme-help-nhs-health-costs">the Welsh Government website</a></li>
  <li>on <a href="https://www.ngicns.scot.nhs.uk/nhsservices/adults/surgery/claiming-travel-subsistence-expenses/">the NGICNS website</a> (Scotland only)</li>
  <li>on <a href="http://www.hscbusiness.hscni.net/pdf/Expenses.pdf">the HSC Northern Ireland website</a></li>
</ul>